_:Nf782284b2c194886884c03061b882318 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Jade Botterill was appointed Assistant Whip, House of Commons on 7 September 2025. She was elected as the MP for Ossett and Denby Dale in July 2024.</p>\n" .
